Then there's the fact that "ours is a heal", but technically, ours isn't really a heal because it takes away so much life in the beginning anyways. 

Only advantage of ours that i've thought of is ours doesn't cost mana, so we can keep fighting. I haven't looked at difference in re-use time. I'm not trying to complain, i love necros, but you guys can all tell me to go be a wizzy anyways, hehe.

What do you guys think


